lastCommit.message:
fix: Cloudflare Pages build configuration

- Fix protocol docs generator to handle empty schemas directory
- Add Node.js engine requirements to package.json (>=18.0.0)
- Create wrangler.toml for Cloudflare Pages configuration
- Add .nvmrc file for Node.js version management
- Update .gitignore to exclude .nvmrc and build artifacts
- Specify build environment variables for Cloudflare Pages

Fixes build failures in Cloudflare Pages deployment
